298
00:17:48,099 --> 00:17:48,899
Rest early.

299
00:17:48,899 --> 00:17:49,538
Let's go.

300
00:18:00,258 --> 00:18:02,099
Mr. Yao, it's time to get off work

301
00:18:02,139 --> 00:18:03,258
