302
00:18:03,899 --> 00:18:07,018
Okay, Mr. Mai and I will
come to pick you up.

303
00:18:14,619 --> 00:18:16,698
Guys, thank you for your hard work.

304
00:18:17,458 --> 00:18:19,258
Except for those
who need to stay on duty,

305
00:18:19,339 --> 00:18:20,298
the rest of you

306
